After many years of healing the hurt, clerics and paladins become more<br>
proficient at their task, and find themselves able to heal more then one<br>
person at a time.  Please note that the same restrictions regarding<br>
healing those of other alignments apply to this as for one-on-one healing<br>
spells.<br>
